                    ·match_done ·m_5, ·ƒ_fail, fn ·v_6, ·scope, ·state:
                      ·load ·scope, ·id'a', fn a, ·scope:
                        ·ƒ_cont a, ·state
        fn ·v_7, ·scope, ·state: ·ƒ_cont ·v_7, ·state

